{"id":16799,"date":"2019-04-13T21:07:27","date_gmt":"2019-04-13T14:07:27","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=16799"},"modified":"2019-11-29T17:01:29","modified_gmt":"2019-11-29T10:01:29","slug":"gui-mail-hang-loat-mien-phi-voi-groundhogg","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/gui-mail-hang-loat-mien-phi-voi-groundhogg","title":{"rendered":"Groundhogg: G\u1eedi mail h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><strong>Groundhogg \u0111ang t\u1ea1o ra l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng m\u1edbi khi cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 g\u1eedi mail h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Email list l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 g\u1eedi email lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m MailChimp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00ean phong v\u1ec1 email marketing mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 doanh thu kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn ng\u00e0y nay.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng MailChimp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o Squeeze Page mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/usecase\/huong-dan-su-dung-mailchimp-tao-squeeze-page\/\" target=\"_blank\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng MailChimp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o Squeeze Page mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Mailchimp.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ecdc t\u1eadp theo th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Groundhogg (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/groundhogg\" target=\"_blank\">Groundhogg<\/a> c\u0169ng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n Groundhoog c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n danh b\u1ea1 (contact) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1eedi email.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Groundhogg l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"978\" height=\"513\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Groundhogg-la-gi.png\" alt=\"Groundhogg l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" class=\"wp-image-16836\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Groundhogg-la-gi.png 978w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Groundhogg-la-gi-218x114.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Groundhogg-la-gi-300x157.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Groundhogg-la-gi-700x367.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Groundhogg-la-gi-768x403.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 978px) 100vw, 978px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"\/out\/groundhogg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Groundhogg (opens in a new tab)\">Groundhogg<\/a><\/strong> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t plugin mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a WordPress \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t CRM (qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng), email marketing v\u00e0 marketing t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem Groundhogg nh\u01b0 Mailchimp ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Groundhogg<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Groundhogg r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00ec ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o WordPress n\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>WordPress<\/strong>. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 host v\u00e0 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WordPress \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0i Groundhogg plugin.<\/li><li><strong>SMTP<\/strong>. Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 SMTP email c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd v\u00e0o th\u01b0 m\u1ee5c spam c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. SMTP mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Mailgun (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.mailgun.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">Mailgun<\/a><\/strong>, <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Sparkpost (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/sparkpost.com\" target=\"_blank\">Sparkpost<\/a><\/strong> hay tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Amazon SES (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/aws.amazon.com\/ses\/\" target=\"_blank\">Amazon SES<\/a><\/strong>, <strong>Sendgrid<\/strong>,&#8230; N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 h\u00e3y t\u1ea1o ngay v\u00ec th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng Groundhogg b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n SMTP \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi mail th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. D\u00f9ng plugin <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"WP Mail SMTP by WPForms (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/wp-mail-smtp\/\" target=\"_blank\">WP Mail SMTP by WPForms<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n SMTP c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh b\u1ea1n.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>G\u1eedi mail h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Groundhogg cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n import contact kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n n\u00ean n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng contact l\u1edbn th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i import v\u00e0o Groundhogg v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng email broadcast \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eedi email.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1<\/strong>: Important contact v\u00e0o Groundhogg<\/li><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2<\/strong>: T\u1ea1o email m\u1eabu (email b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi)<\/li><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3<\/strong>: Broadcast &gt; Schedule Broadcast<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"566\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg-1024x566.png\" alt=\"Schedule Broadcast cua Groundhogg\" class=\"wp-image-16837\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg-1024x566.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg-218x120.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg-300x166.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg-700x387.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg-768x424.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Schedule-Broadcast-cua-Groundhogg.png 1059w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>G\u1eedi mail h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Groundhogg r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Email marketing t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 CRM<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng \u1edf t\u00ednh n\u0103ng g\u1eedi mail h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, Groundhogg c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t <strong>Autoresponder<\/strong> gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u1eedi email t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o Groundhogg form v\u00e0 nh\u00fang v\u00e0o website b\u1eb1ng <strong>shortcode<\/strong> hay <strong>JavaScript<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Groundhogg d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o TAG \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00e1c funnel (Groundhogg \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho quy tr\u00ecnh g\u1eedi email t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 FUNNEL).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, Groundhogg \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng funnel m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 Welcome funnel, Lead Magnet Download,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"406\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg-1024x406.png\" alt=\"Funnel cua GroundHogg\" class=\"wp-image-16838\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg-1024x406.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg-218x86.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg-300x119.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg-700x278.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg-768x305.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-cua-GroundHogg.png 1717w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e1c funnel t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n cho b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o nhanh h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi email drip t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0m theo nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Ch\u1ecdn funnel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Groundhogg thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n hay b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. (B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh funnel c\u1ee7a Groundhogg \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh)<\/li><li>T\u1ea1o form \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd. C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o form gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 contact form 7, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen.<\/li><li>T\u1ea1o email m\u1eabu \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a funnel<\/li><li>Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp quy t\u1eafc g\u1eedi nh\u01b0 ch\u1edd 1 ng\u00e0y, m\u1edf link trong mail, m\u1edf email,&#8230;<\/li><li>Ch\u00e8n form v\u00e0o trang b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n<\/li><li>Xong, m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Groundhogg s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ea1y n\u1ec1n<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"501\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg-1024x501.png\" alt=\"g\u1eedi email h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Groundhogg\" class=\"wp-image-16841\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg-1024x501.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg-218x107.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg-300x147.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg-700x343.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg-768x376.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Funnel-Welcome-cua-GroundHogg.png 1754w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>M\u1ed9t Funnel c\u1ee7a Groundhogg<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"highlight\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: B\u1ea1n b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t xong t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n SMTP tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1o funnel v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng Groundhogg.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>B\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed cho Groundhogg trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0o<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00f9 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0ng Groundhogg ki\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn t\u1eeb vi\u00eac b\u00e1n Extention.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c plugin kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Gravity Form, Contact Form 7, Caldera Form, Ninja Form, Twillio,&#8230; Hay c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng cao c\u1ea5p hiwn nh\u01b0 Lead Scoring, Form Styling, Social Proof. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c extension n\u00e0y. C\u00e1c extention th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1. Tham kh\u1ea3o t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.groundhogg.io\/downloads\/category\/add-ons\/?aff=40\" target=\"_blank\">Extention c\u1ee7a Groundhogg t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"268\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard-1024x268.png\" alt=\"GroundHogg SMS va Email Credit dashboard\" class=\"wp-image-16839\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard-1024x268.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard-218x57.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard-300x79.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard-700x183.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard-768x201.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/GroundHogg-SMS-va-Email-Credit-dashboard.png 1703w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Paste key c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng Groundhogg, r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m khi d\u00f9ng Groundhogg<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>C\u00e1c credit c\u1ee7a Groundhogg l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. <strong>$9.99 cho 20.000 email<\/strong> v\u00e0 credit s\u1ebd trong t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ebft. So v\u1edbi Amazon SES th\u00ec cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 <strong>import v\u00e0 export funnel <\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n funnel c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean ch\u1ee3 funnel c\u1ee7a Groundhogg n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Groundhogg partner.<\/li><li>Tuy Groundhogg kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n email g\u1eedi nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed SMTP c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00ed d\u1ee5 g\u00f3i Mailgun mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n b\u1ea1n 10.000 email hay Amazon SES tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed <strong>0.1$<\/strong> cho <strong>1.000<\/strong> email. V\u00ec v\u1eady, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, SMTP r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/li><li>Groundhogg kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 HTTP request.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Groundhogg tr\u00ean <strong>domain ch\u00ednh<\/strong> thay v\u00ec <strong>subdomain<\/strong> v\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Groundhogg d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Shortcode v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n quy\u1ec1n User.<\/li><li>GroudHogg ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o <strong>TAG<\/strong>, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm r\u00f5 c\u00e1ch th\u00eam TAG, b\u1ecf TAG theo t\u1eebng h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 Groundhogg ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg-1024x534.png\" alt=\"Pricing email credit GroundHogg\" class=\"wp-image-16843\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg-1024x534.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg-218x114.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg-300x156.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg-700x365.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg-768x400.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Pricing-email-credit-GroundHogg.png 1441w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed 1 l\u1ea7n Email Credit c\u1ee7a Groundhogg (tham kh\u1ea3o)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Groundhogg r\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u1edbi t\u00ednh n\u0103ng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi mail h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n (gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf SMTP c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chi ph\u00ed khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn, nh\u01b0ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng m\u1edbi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 app di \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn xem Groundhogg c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng d\u00f9ng hay kh\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00e0i vi\u1ebfy nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Groundhogg cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi mail h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng Wordpress v\u00e0 SMTP c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. M\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean n\u0103ng k\u00fd thay th\u1ebf Mailchimp.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":16834,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"close","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[198],"tags":[194],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/gui-mail-hang-loat-voi-GroundHogg.png",1150,575,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/gui-mail-hang-loat-voi-GroundHogg-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/gui-mail-hang-loat